885
00:48:55,520 --> 00:48:57,190
You shut up!

886
00:48:57,430 --> 00:48:58,710
What was my job?

887
00:48:58,710 --> 00:48:59,120
Huh?

888
00:48:59,120 --> 00:48:59,800
What was it?

889
00:48:59,800 --> 00:49:01,190
The chief of the Security Section, OK?

890
00:49:01,190 --> 00:49:02,800
I got some skills.

891
00:49:02,800 --> 00:49:03,840
