895
00:49:08,320 --> 00:49:10,390
Anyway, I was doing better than you.

896
00:49:10,390 --> 00:49:11,520
Don't waste time.

897
00:49:12,320 --> 00:49:13,150
Come on.

898
00:49:13,150 --> 00:49:13,760
