901
00:49:18,280 --> 00:49:19,800
Would I? Huh?

902
00:49:19,800 --> 00:49:20,150
Go on.

903
00:49:20,470 --> 00:49:23,840
That guy came out of this community,
wearing slippers.

904
00:49:23,840 --> 00:49:24,600
What kind of slippers?

905
00:49:25,760 --> 00:49:27,000
What kind of slippers?

906
00:49:27,080 --> 00:49:28,360
Non-peep-toe slippers.

907
00:49:28,360 --> 00:49:28,910
What color?

908
00:49:28,910 --> 00:49:30,230
Color of what?

909
00:49:30,230 --> 00:49:31,520
Toes?

910
00:49:31,520 --> 00:49:32,670
Slippers, I mean.

911
00:49:33,360 --> 00:49:35,080
What a weird question!

912
00:49:35,080 --> 00:49:36,150
You didn't see that?

913
00:49:36,150 --> 00:49:37,430
How... How could I…?

914
00:49:37,430 --> 00:49:37,870
I just...

915
00:49:37,870 --> 00:49:38,470
What the heck!

916
00:49:38,470 --> 00:49:39,760
Jianchun,
what does that guy look like?

917
00:49:39,760 --> 00:49:40,520
Do you still remember?

918
00:49:41,390 --> 00:49:42,710
A rough image.

919
00:49:45,000 --> 00:49:45,600
My son is back.

920
00:49:47,840 --> 00:49:48,280
Uncle Biao.

921
00:49:48,910 --> 00:49:49,840
You're back, Bei.

922
00:49:50,520 --> 00:49:51,520
How are you prepared for the exam?

923
00:49:51,520 --> 00:49:52,390
Can you pass it?

924
00:49:52,390 --> 00:49:53,150
Not bad.

925
00:49:53,150 --> 00:49:54,470
My son is clever.

926
00:49:55,230 --> 00:49:56,080
Why are you back so late?

927
00:49:56,360 --> 00:49:57,230
I did some shopping.

928
00:49:58,120 --> 00:49:58,870
Having a girlfriend?

929
00:49:59,670 --> 00:50:00,040
No.

930
00:50:00,390 --> 00:50:00,950
Don't tease him.

931
00:50:01,470 --> 00:50:01,910
This is Mr. Ma.

932
00:50:02,120 --> 00:50:02,520
Mr. Ma.

933
00:50:02,520 --> 00:50:03,230
This is Mr. Xing.

934
00:50:03,230 --> 00:50:04,150
Hello, Mr. Xing.

935
00:50:04,150 --> 00:50:05,190
He looks like you, Wang.

936
00:50:05,190 --> 00:50:07,840
I mean, you're getting more
like your father, young man.

937
00:50:07,840 --> 00:50:09,870
I was lost in chatting
that I forgot to make dinner for him.

938
00:50:09,870 --> 00:50:10,630
It's OK, Dad.

939
00:50:10,630 --> 00:50:11,320
Go on with your conversation.

940
00:50:11,320 --> 00:50:11,800
I'll make dinner later.

941
00:50:11,800 --> 00:50:12,560
