can you get us your drawing board?

944
00:50:17,800 --> 00:50:18,840
What do you want it for?

945
00:50:29,360 --> 00:50:30,120
The mouth...

946
00:50:30,910 --> 00:50:32,360
Drooping a little bit.

947
00:50:33,470 --> 00:50:34,000
OK.

948
00:50:35,950 --> 00:50:36,560
You know what?

949
00:50:36,840 --> 00:50:38,120
Bei... He really has a painting talent.

950
00:50:40,870 --> 00:50:41,760
Can you confirm this?

951
00:50:42,120 --> 00:50:43,430
Look. I can almost confirm.

952
00:50:45,190 --> 00:50:46,520
The one you nearly caught in the garage?

953
00:50:46,760 --> 00:50:47,800
I didn't see him clearly.

954
00:50:47,800 --> 00:50:49,080
He crawled through the fields.

955
00:50:49,080 --> 00:50:50,000
