1009
00:52:35,630 --> 00:52:36,520
Well, listen to me.

1010
00:52:36,520 --> 00:52:37,630
Just a token of my care.

1011
00:52:37,840 --> 00:52:38,840
Take the money back.

1012
00:52:39,120 --> 00:52:40,360
