1015
00:52:51,710 --> 00:52:52,600
Sounds closer.

1016
00:52:53,280 --> 00:52:53,760
Got it?

1017
00:52:57,000 --> 00:52:57,760
I...

1018
00:52:58,000 --> 00:53:00,150
